1. Which of the following points is important to align on when creating an execution plan?
Solution : A. Red flags

2. When delegating responsibilities to your report, you say, "Great, we've agreed that you'll send me the assignment on Friday." What else should you include?
Solution : D. All of the above

3. When your report misses a deadline and is struggling with a task, the first thing to do to get the project back on track is:
Solution : D. Ask other teammates to lend a hand
